		A decently simple text editor built in C++.

		aed is written by Ariston Lorenzo.

		Copyright 2023 Ariston Lorenzo. See COPYRIGHT.


WHAT IS aed?

aed is just a text editor made to keep me from getting bored. There are many
features from within Emacs and Neovim that I had always wanted together so this
gives me a chance to merge these together into one piece of software.
